Preconditions:
- The arrays `tops` and `bottoms` must have the same length.
- The arrays `tops` and `bottoms` must not be empty.

Postconditions:
- If it is possible to make all the values in `tops` the same or all the values in `bottoms` the same, return the minimum number of rotations required.
- If it is not possible to make all the values in `tops` the same or all the values in `bottoms` the same, return `-1`.